      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/queryInterface?q=4">Lowest stock price for each company in the latest one year. </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="/queryInterface?q=5">List the ids of companies along with their name who have the average stock price lesser than the lowest of Google in the latest one year. </a>
      </li>
   </div> 
<div id="background"></div>
</div>

